I have a very slow connection over here in NZ and therefore there is no reason to hurry.  One episode every two or three days will be more than adequate, especially since X & Xtra Factor Series 6 is due to start before the end of August.  

Auditions for X Factor started in June - Dannii Minogue is having a baby and Cheryl Cole has been excused due to a stress related illness.  We will see stand-in Judges including Natalie Imbruglia, Pixie Lott, Katy Perry and we also have a new Xtra Factor presenter Konnie Hug.
Edit:  Should have said, X Factor Series 7 ... it actually starts on Saturday 21st August @ 8.30pm UK time.
